","id":25284},"last_reply_by":"swsh007","last_touched":1635602287,"title":"2021 年 10 月，在 Ubuntu Linux 上如何使用微信 ？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/811705","created":1635565471,"deleted":0,"content":"之前一直在 Ubuntu 上用浏览器使用微信网页版。\r\n但是从最近开始（貌似是微信和 WeChat 分家有关？），web 版微信不让登录了。\r\n\r\n我人在海外，由于微信手机号用的国外号码，所以我被分到了 wechat 。\r\n然而，我试了把手机号码换回国内号码，并且微信 app 也明确提示了我从 wechat 转为微信，我依然不能登录网页版。\r\n\r\n因为工作原因我必须使用 Ubuntu ，请问使用微信的最佳姿势是什么？","content_rendered":"<p>之前一直在 Ubuntu 上用浏览器使用微信网页版。\n但是从最近开始（貌似是微信和 WeChat 分家有关？），web 版微信不让登录了。</p>\n<p>我人在海外，由于微信手机号用的国外号码，所以我被分到了 wechat 。\n然而，我试了把手机号码换回国内号码，并且微信 app 也明确提示了我从 wechat 转为微信，我依然不能登录网页版。</p>\n<p>因为工作原因我必须使用 Ubuntu ，请问使用微信的最佳姿势是什么？</p>\n","last_modified":1635565471,"replies":39,"id":811705},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1629391393","name":"qna","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1629391393","title":"问与答","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","topics":177888,"footer":"","header":"一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。","title_alternative":"Questions and Answers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","stars":3342,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"lo0p","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d979abd8f33df8b55a38dce69e985bb1?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/lo0p","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1582175722,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d979abd8f33df8b55a38dce69e985bb1?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d979abd8f33df8b55a38dce69e985bb1?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":470672},"last_reply_by":"20160409","last_touched":1635595550,"title":"win11 推送了，现在 win11 好用吗？可以更新吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/811676","created":1635558303,"deleted":0,"content":"如上题，今天早上过来公司电脑推送 win11 ，状态栏上一直有个更新图标，很烦。","content_rendered":"<p>如上题，今天早上过来公司电脑推送 win11 ，状态栏上一直有个更新图标，很烦。</p>\n","last_modified":1635558303,"replies":30,"id":811676},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_large.png?m=1628872984","name":"share","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_normal.png?m=1628872984","title":"分享发现","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/share","topics":34508,"footer":"","header":"分享你看到的好玩的，有信息量的，欢迎从这里获取灵感。","title_alternative":"Share","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c74d/97b0/16_mini.png?m=1628872984","stars":4622,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":16,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"username":"fengmenggaokao","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d3ad0ccf02206dc86341d96517fb6514?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/fengmenggaokao","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1419999707,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d3ad0ccf02206dc86341d96517fb6514?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d3ad0ccf02206dc86341d96517fb6514?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":89279},"last_reply_by":"WebKit","last_touched":1635602655,"title":"请各位老哥不要再宣传所谓的 google voice 永久保号了，误人子弟","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/811678","created":1635559027,"deleted":0,"content":"# 网传的 google voice 永久保号步骤\r\n\r\n1. 10 美金购买新号码\r\n2. 20 美金把原来的号码变成 permanent\r\n\r\n# 问题所在\r\n\t\r\n20 美金只是保留你原来的号码所花费的金额，在花费 10 美金购买新的号码后，你的主号码会变成新号码，旧号码不能打电话发短信，并且保留 90 天，如果想要一直保留，需要花费 20 美金。这里永久的意思不是一直持有。只是和原来没有购买新号码一样的保号政策。\r\n\r\n# 补充点\r\n\r\n1. 10 美金只是购买新号码费用，根据你选择号码的所在州不同，会收取一定的税，我自己被收了百分之 20 的税\r\n2. 新买号码不能退款，我和客服 battle 了很大一阵，给我了退费政策 https://support.google.com/voice/answer/7576316?hl=en#zippy=%2Cnon-refundable-requests 注意下面的不可退款的 situation\r\n\r\n# 总结\r\n\r\n花钱只是买新号码，不是永久保号","content_rendered":"<h1>网传的 google voice 永久保号步骤</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>10 美金购买新号码</li>\n<li>20 美金把原来的号码变成 permanent</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>问题所在</h1>\n<p>20 美金只是保留你原来的号码所花费的金额，在花费 10 美金购买新的号码后，你的主号码会变成新号码，旧号码不能打电话发短信，并且保留 90 天，如果想要一直保留，需要花费 20 美金。这里永久的意思不是一直持有。只是和原来没有购买新号码一样的保号政策。</p>\n<h1>补充点</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>10 美金只是购买新号码费用，根据你选择号码的所在州不同，会收取一定的税，我自己被收了百分之 20 的税</li>\n<li>新买号码不能退款，我和客服 battle 了很大一阵，给我了退费政策 <a href=\"https://support.google.com/voice/answer/7576316?hl=en#zippy=%2Cnon-refundable-requests\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://support.google.com/voice/answer/7576316?hl=en#zippy=%2Cnon-refundable-requests</a> 注意下面的不可退款的 situation</li>\n</ol>\n<h1>总结</h1>\n<p>花钱只是买新号码，不是永久保号</p>\n","last_modified":1635559027,"replies":29,"id":811678},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":16566,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":1979,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"username":"xtx","website":"","github":"","psn":"","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1266/8b36/439903_mini.png?m=1600317675","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xtx","tagline":"血液的作用之一是为信仰付出代价。","twitter":"","created":1567694914,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1266/8b36/439903_mini.png?m=1600317675","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1266/8b36/439903_mini.png?m=1600317675","location":"","btc":"","id":439903},"last_reply_by":"pdog18","last_touched":1635582802,"title":"apple watch 更新到 8.1 后洗手监测失效？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/811669","created":1635555622,"deleted":0,"content":"前些天到手的 aw7 ，当时系统是 8.01 ，洗手监测是有效的，然后 26 号更新到 8.1 之后，再也没有一次成功过，测试了很多遍，洗手的时候可以看到 aw 显示有麦克风启用，说明监测到了水声，但是没有启动倒计时，不知道各位的是否正常？","content_rendered":"<p>前些天到手的 aw7 ，当时系统是 8.01 ，洗手监测是有效的，然后 26 号更新到 8.1 之后，再也没有一次成功过，测试了很多遍，洗手的时候可以看到 aw 显示有麦克风启用，说明监测到了水声，但是没有启动倒计时，不知道各位的是否正常？</p>\n","last